RESERVATION_LOCKBOX_CODE_NOTES: You will use the lockbox to the right of the door
UNIT_LOCKBOX_NOTES: You will use the lockbox to the right of the door
RESERVATION_UNIT_ADDRESS_ADDRESS_1: 33 Black Point Road DO NOT USE GPS
RESERVATION_DRIVING_DIRECTIONS:
1) Turn left at the blinking light onto Pritham Ave (Rt 15 north).
2) Continue on this road for about 20 minutes into the town of Rockwood.
3) Cross the Moose River Bridge on your right (after the Moose River Country Store). Go right at the end of the bridge and follow the road for about 2.6 miles.
4) Turn right onto Murray Rd. 
5) At the first fork, take a left on Black Point Rd. Go to the bottom of the hill and take a right at the T.
6) The physical address is 33 Black Point Rd, Tomhegan.
UNIT_PARKING_NOTES: Parking is available for four cars and two trailers.
